01:59:14.375 --> 01:59:17.125
"Except that I wasn't happy with myself."

01:59:19.333 --> 01:59:21.416
"All I saw were my shortcomings."

01:59:22.541 --> 01:59:25.250
"I was so caught up
with what I don't have,

01:59:25.875 --> 01:59:31.291
